Procedure.Subject: CAHEL Ultra Light 83 CPB Final Specifications
Procedure.Brief_Summary: CAHEL Ultra Light 83 started production on October 1, Phase III was run the week of 10/16/90. An evaluation of the Phase X9903 data and weekly tar/CATE data indicates that Holes Open/Holes Closed Draft and FTC Tar specifications should be modified. Recommended final specifications are attached.
